
                    ########################################
                    Extra Link Libraries for Tinker on Linux
                    ########################################

       This directory contains any extra object libraries to be included
       when linking Tinker under Linux. For example, they could be static
       compiler libraries, static version of FFTW libraries, etc.

       Unless otherwise specified, libraries are for Intel x86_64 CPUs.
       There is no quadmath library for ARM CPUs, and it is not needed to
       build functional ARM executables.

